This paper discusses the ethical development and governance of AI, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also touches upon the practical implementation of ethical principles, which could be relevant to Robotics (cs.RO) and Cybersecurity (cs.CY). Additionally, the paper discusses the need for accountability mechanisms, which could be relevant to Ethics in Technology (cs.ET) and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
